            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My sister’s daughter is studying in the primary branch of the school who is taking transportation service from school. Earlier there was no issue in the pickup and drop timing of child but recently they changed the dropping timings of a 4 year kid to 4pm. Where as the closing time of school is 2pm for students. Now child is reaching home after 2 hours, which was earlier 45 minutes. And we complain about this to the principal. I was astonished to hear the reply, she was saying that their regular small vehicles are busy in elections now a days. Is this the way school are managing by the principals, who’s priorities are elections rather than the students.Pathetic",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
