            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The journey with Delhi World Public school, Greater Noida has been a wonderful experience throughout my son's schooling. The teachers and management are all experienced & supportive and help in the overall grooming of the child. With a well balanced teacher Student ratio in every class, every student gets proper attention. Wishing the whole team of DWPS the very best of luck.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
