            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "DPS World school Noida extension is one of the best school, as of now there are multiple school which is running in Noida extension but as per my understanding this is one of the best school. to understand it better you can go there and understand the same. I m very much satisfied with the management, and Staff members here. The school is very collaborative and working hard towards brushing up the skills of the students. I have a good time herein. This school provides the best platform for the students to learn the things in an innovative way which leads in the enhancement of the knowledge and abilities of a students. To make your children 'future oriented\" go up with it.",
